{"tid":2185813,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[開學了］契哥馬浚偉：先生早 校長早 各位早。。。","createTime":"2020-09-02T13:41:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-03T10:27:32.000Z","uid":56716,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d63ffa89c32af505cfc8947d57d5a03f76d7040b","tid":2185813,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T13:41:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b4JirMS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb4JirMS.png&h=7555c207&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jc14nkc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJc14nkc.png&h=50d7e92b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n曾勇奪我最喜愛電視男角色，暨著名歌手兼任導演並被視為上屆金像獎最佳導演頂頭大熱兼王家衛最強競敵的馬浚偉（契哥），繼數月前北京大學碩士畢業後，不久前又獲香港浸會大學中醫藥學院取錄，為期兩年的課程昨天正式開學。契哥日前出席線上迎新會，40有8的契哥看起來依舊俊朗年輕，未知其同班同學上課時看見如此俊俏的校草會不會分心呢？<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cXbsj9w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcXbsj9w.png&h=ca7d4ef4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wZx7j9w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwZx7j9w.png&h=55812738&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zjks4Bc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZjks4Bc.jpg&h=65364bc9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qKWgdux.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqKWgdux.jpg&h=541b506e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a314294974385380d276089336df8ffd0e06ffa3","tid":2185813,"uid":122167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T13:41:58.000Z","msg":"吉吉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0670a4267dec7462538e217de1e58672e682cca","tid":2185813,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a314294974385380d276089336df8ffd0e06ffa3","t